525
00:35:55,630 --> 00:35:57,760
Hello.

526
00:36:02,010 --> 00:36:05,060
Ah, yes. Hello.

527
00:36:09,600 --> 00:36:12,040
Excuse me, then.

528
00:36:19,390 --> 00:36:22,000
I wonder if that's the Chairman's girlfriend.

529
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:24,870
Let's go in, Dan Dan.

530
00:36:24,870 --> 00:36:28,710
You go in first. I'm going to use the restroom.

531
00:36:28,710 --> 00:36:31,990
Okay.

532
00:36:38,930 --> 00:36:41,640
Who's she to link arms with the Chairman?

533
00:36:41,640 --> 00:36:44,780
Who is that woman?

534
00:36:52,180 --> 00:36:55,520
There's someone you have to meet tomorrow with me.

535
00:36:55,520 --> 00:36:58,230
Who is it?

536
00:36:58,230 --> 00:37:02,220
