540
00:37:17,860 --> 00:37:21,270
It'll be bad if you say you don't like her later on.

541
00:37:21,270 --> 00:37:25,720
Dad, it hasn't been too long since you broke up with Ms. Park! How could you meet some other woman?

542
00:37:25,720 --> 00:37:28,210
I don't think this is right at all.

543
00:37:28,210 --> 00:37:30,240
Se Jong, what do you think?

544
00:37:30,240 --> 00:37:33,040
I agree with my brother.

545
00:37:33,040 --> 00:37:38,170
Se Chan and Se Jong, I'm not saying I'm going to move forward with her right away.

546
00:37:38,170 --> 00:37:40,940
I just want you guys to meet her first.

547
00:37:40,940 --> 00:37:44,410
If you say you don't like her after meeting her, I'll reconsider.

548
00:37:44,410 --> 00:37:47,190
Let's go see her tomorrow together, okay?

549
00:37:47,220 --> 00:37:50,070
Okay, Dad.

550
00:37:50,070 --> 00:37:55,220
Hey, Lee Se Chan, Lee Se Jong, do you want our dad to live alone forever?

551
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:58,490
Dad needs to meet with many people too.

552
00:37:58,490 --> 00:38:00,850
Okay, then let's meet her.

553
00:38:00,850 --> 00:38:04,090
I'm sure she won't be good as Ms. Park.

554
00:38:04,090 --> 00:38:08,570
There will be no girlfriend that's better than Ms. Park.

555
00:38:14,040 --> 00:38:16,570
It feels like spring now.

556
00:38:16,570 --> 00:38:19,440
