558
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:28,850
Ah, yes. You're right.

559
00:38:28,850 --> 00:38:33,310
Dan Dan, to tell you the truth,

560
00:38:33,310 --> 00:38:36,610
I'm so happy that I met you again.

561
00:38:36,610 --> 00:38:42,930
I liked you when we were in school too. Did you know?

562
00:38:45,030 --> 00:38:49,670
